# WorkflowAgent Guardrails

Read `.cursor/skills/ai-sdk-v7-workflow-agent/SKILL.md` before modifying code in this project.

**Never use in this project:** `DurableAgent`, `ToolLoopAgent`, `maxSteps`, `toolApproval`, `experimental_context`, `experimental_output`, `collectUIMessages`, `agent.generate()`.

**Always use:** `WorkflowAgent` (`@ai-sdk/workflow`), `needsApproval`, `stopWhen: isStepCount(n)`, `runtimeContext` + `toolsContext`, `'use workflow'` / `'use step'`, `ModelCallStreamPart` + `createModelCallToUIChunkTransform()`.
